Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP「FLY」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No matter what happens, It’s OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.23,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because we are the best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:23.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are the best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:26.19,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Nobody can ever stop us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because we are the best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.07,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, touch the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:30.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}ビルディング伸びる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.53,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}狭い空見上げ Close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:37.04,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The next moment 広がる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:40.08,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}踏み出せば I’ll have a new experience
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:41.66,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We go back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But we are who we are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.79,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}見失わず 前へ Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.17,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Count on you, flyin’ up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:51.51,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anywhere, we can handle everything so well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.97,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}常に冷静に Manage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.64,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}平凡な檻からFly away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:55.68,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just like a business
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.18,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}世界を見極め Negotiate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.93,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To live is continuously to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until I die, no end in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.27,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe in our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:08.07,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繋がってる　確かなパス
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:10.86,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your power still flows into me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.70,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感じてる　大切なものをこの肩に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.20,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}きみとならFly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:20.66,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I decided to become a sage of the stars, oh like you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.54,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Push forward!! Pu- Push forward!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Flyin’ high!! Fl- Flyin’ high!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}止まる事ない二つのタイムライン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.30,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}変えていく　さあ二人でRight now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.05,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.14,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on! Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:41.10,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}何処までもきみとFly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.69,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论发生什么 都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.23,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我们是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:23.44,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们是最好的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:26.19,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人能阻挡我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.82,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我们是最好的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.07,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在让我们触摸天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:30.32,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大楼不断向前延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.53,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}仰望狭窄的天空 闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:37.04,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下一刻 是更广阔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:40.08,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要向前踏出一步 就能有全新的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:41.66,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不断折返
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.00,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.79,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不忘初心 继续前行!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.17,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}依靠你 飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:51.51,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论何地 我们都能将完美处理一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.97,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}时刻保持冷静地管理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.64,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}飞离平凡的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:55.68,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就像是做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.18,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}洞察世界以此谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.93,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生活就是不断地学习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.52,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直至死亡 都无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.27,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我相信我们的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:08.07,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那真实连结着的纽带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:10.86,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的力量依然流淌在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.70,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能感受到 肩负着重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.20,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与你一起飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:20.66,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我决定成为星之贤者 就如你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.54,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}噢噢（向前推进!!向前推进!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.58,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}噢噢（飞向高空!!飞向高空!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.71,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}两条永不停止的时间线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.30,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们两人一起改变 就是现在!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.80,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能为你做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.05,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我能与你做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.14,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续前进！继续前进!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:41.10,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与你一起飞翔到任何地方
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「曖昧ガール」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Life is wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.83,0:22:30.04,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Ah！キミがいない日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:33.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ピンクのない桜の花みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:36.21,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}No！それはいや
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:39.92,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}わたしはもう恋をしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:43.80,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ハローハロー　コイワズライさん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:47.05,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}甘酸っぱいスイーツランチタイム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:51.18,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}日曜日の午後はまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:55.02,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}高鳴る鼓動が痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:58.52,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}水たまりをジャンプして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:01.65,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}今日はどこでなにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.53,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ホントはずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:07.41,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ふたりでいたいのに（だめ?）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.87,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}曖昧な距離感でどうしようって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:12.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}どうしたいってmisty days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:16.12,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ときめいて強がって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.42,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ハッとしてパニック!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.80,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ドキドキがバレちゃう、キミに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:24.84,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}曖昧じゃ大胆にいかないし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あたりまえにone-way-love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:30.18,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}恋の途中はいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:34.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ココロとカラダが（今日も）反比例
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:38.10,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}わたし　曖昧ガール
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.94,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}人生是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.83,0:22:30.04,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}啊！没有你的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:33.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就像是失去粉色的樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:36.21,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不！绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:39.92,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我已坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:43.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你好你好 陷入相思的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:47.05,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}酸甜点心的午餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:51.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}星期日的中午
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:55.02,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}激动的心跳感到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:58.52,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一下跳过水洼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:01.65,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}今天要在哪里做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.53,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}其实的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:07.41,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直想要和你两人独处（不行吗?）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.87,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}在暧昧的距离感下该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:12.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}想要做些什么 在迷茫的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:16.12,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那强烈的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.42,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}惊觉的我陷入恐慌!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}被你发现那惊慌失措的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:24.84,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}暧昧又不能过于大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.93,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}理所当然的单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:30.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}在恋爱的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:34.89,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}内心和行动（今天也）呈现反比
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:38.10,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我就是暧昧女孩
